Class CoordinatorPlugin

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.sorbonne_u.components.AbstractPlugin

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RTCoordinatorPlugin

    public class CoordinatorPlugin
extends AbstractSimulatorPlugin
    The class CoordinatorPlugin implements a BCM plug-in for the coordination role in DEVS simulations.

    Description

    In DEVS, coupled simulation models are meant to coordinate the submodels they compose. This plug-in gathers the necessary code to make a BCM component able to hold and execute a coupled simulation model.

    Invariant

     invariant       (architecture == null || architecture.isCoupledModel(getPluginURI()))
 invariant       (smops == null || coordinatedPorts == null) || (smops.size() == coordinatedPorts.size())

    Created on : 2018-06-14

    Author:
    Jacques Malenfant
